From cou.: 6 CTP can be easily hexa-functionalized through nucleophilic substitution reactions22 on the corresponding hexachloride (NPCl2)3 analog leading to a nearly planar system where the phosphorous atoms are almost tetrahedral (sp3) and the nitrogen atoms approach an sp2 geometry.23 CTP moieties exhibit excellent thermal and chemical stabilities and are photochemically and electrochemically inert. As a consequence, they do not interfere with the photophysical and electrochemical properties centered on the grafted redox active chromophores. The easiness of CTP ring functionalization coupled to the structural rigidity of the products makes CTP an attractive core for the construction of multifunctional and robust systems.
From Soup: 6 CTP can be easily hexa-functionalized through nucleophilic substitution reactions 22 on the corresponding hexachloride (NPCl 2 ) 3 analog leading to a nearly planar system where the phosphorous atoms are almost tetrahedral (sp 3 ) and the nitrogen atoms approach an sp 2 geometry. 23 CTP moieties exhibit excellent thermal and chemical stabilities and are photochemically and electrochemically inert. As a consequence, they do not interfere with the photophysical and electrochemical properties centered on the grafted redox active chromophores . The easiness of CTP ring functionalization coupled to the structural rigidity of the products makes CTP an attractive core for the construction of multifunctional and robust systems.
