From cou.: 9 In order to characterize the redox-activated behavior of HV12+, cyclovoltammetric (CV) electrochemical experiments (Fig. 1a) were performed.
From Soup: 9 In order to characterize the redox-activated behavior of HV 12+ , cyclovoltammetric ( CV ) electrochemical experiments ( Fig. 1a ) were performed.
